The delay today does not mean negative consequences in the future.
We do not plan to work "two more to catch up" after the end of the pandemic.
You won't need to work overtime to meet unrealistic deadlines for the current time.
We recognize that circumstances have changed, and we will work to set new goals and timetables, as far as possible.
